name: CNEH
body:
### Canadian Network for Economic History Datasets.
Lest we lose any of these.

### Why
The Canadian Network for Economic History meets every 18 months to present and discuss recent research in economic history.


### Who
@shawnday maintains these files and attempts to maintain the root [CNEH website](http://economichistory.ca.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
